%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwildest-outfits-harry-styles-best-fashion-moments%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHarry%20Styles%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20pre-loved%20outfit%20sourced%20from%20eBay%20for%20a%20shoot%20for%20his%20latest%20album%20launch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22SZA%20at%20the%202026%20Met%20Gala%20wearing%20an%20outfit%20sourced%20on%20eBay.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a05e430abc4e9d88574a0c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESZA's%20outfit%20at%20the%202026%20Met%20Gala%20was%20sourced%20from%20eBay.%3Cp%3EMike%20Coppola%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reason%20why%20we've%20done%20that%20is%20so%20that%20we%20can%20put%20pre-loved%20fashion%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20some%20of%20these%20really%20big%20fashion%20moments%20and%20get%20people%20to%20think%20about%20fashion%20really%20differently%2C%26quot%3B%20Keoghan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22038f3a57-4e95-4a2d-8e86-9c70938a25cf%5C%22%3EFierce%20competition%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20trendy%20collaborations%20and%20the%20popularity%20of%20pre-loved%20fashion%20among%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-secondhand-shopping-luxury-high-end-preloved-items-report-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGen%20Z%20consumers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Keoghan%20said%20eBay%20does%20not%20have%20a%20specific%20core%20customer%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20got%20all%20of%20the%20other%20categories%2C%20which%20I%20think%20for%20us%20is%20like%20our%20superpower%20because%20you%20can%20come%20and%20buy%20fashion%20and%20you%20can%20also%20go%20and%20buy%20or%20sell%20a%20desk%20or%20a%20sofa%2C%26quot%3B%20Keoghan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20eBay's%20launch%2C%20younger%20companies%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmilda-mitkute-vinted-cofounder-lithuania-s