ons%20crazy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side%20by%20side%20of%20Daina%20Jenkins%20before%20surgery%20and%20the%20ChatGPT%20image%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a074e77ecd7cc1332bb026d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBefore%20getting%20a%20facelift%2C%20Daina%20Jenkins%2C%20pictured%20on%20the%20left%20prior%20to%20surgery%2C%20asked%20ChatGPT%20what%20it%20would%20look%20like.%20The%20image%2C%20on%20the%20right%2C%20looked%20nothing%20like%20her%20final%20result.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Daina%20Jenkins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPatients%20are%20turning%20to%20AI%20for%20inspiration%20in%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplastic-surgery-fat-from-dead-people-alloclae-corporate-ozempic-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplastic%20surgery%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20dermatology.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20results%2C%20doctors%20say%2C%20are%20often%20physically%20impossible%20or%20unsafe.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20the%20latest%20example%20of%20how%20technology%20is%20growing%20the%20gap%20between%20beauty%20expectations%20and%20reality.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUnreal%20expectations%20are%20par%20for%20the%20course%20in%20cosmetic%20dermatologist%20Dr.%20Rachel%20Westbay's%20line%20of%20work.%20Patients%20regularly%20bring%20in%20photos%20of%20celebrities%20or%20their%20younger%20selves%2C%20asking%20her%20to%20work%20her%20magic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20she%20encountered%20something%20entirely%20new%20when%20a%20patient%20brought%20into%20her%20Upper%20East%20Side%20office%20what%20Westbay%20described%20as%20a%20caricature.%20The%20image%20was%20cartoonish%2C%20with%20lips%20too%20full%20for%20her%20face%20and%20enlarged%2C%20doll-like%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20creator%20was%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20saying%20I%20want%20to%20look%20like%20Ariel%20from%20'The%20Little%20Mermaid%2C'%26quot%3B%20Westbay%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20shocked.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArtificial%20intelligence%20is%20increasingly%20entering%20doctors'%20offices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20letting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplastic-surgery-c-suite-executives-beauty-trends-look-younger-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eplastic%20surgeons%20and%20dermatologists%3C%2Fa%3E%20be%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bafter%2C%26quot%3B%20patients%20are%20prompting%20AI%20image%20generators%20to%20create%20their%20ideal%20versions%20of%20themselves.%20Some%20use%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-chatgpt-images-2-image-generator-fake-pictures-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChatGPT%20or%20Nano%20Banana%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20others%20use%20specialized%20apps%20and%20AI%20filters.%20It's%20the%20latest%20example%20of%20how%20technology%2C%20like%20Snapchat%20filters%20and%20Photoshop%20before%20it%2C%20is%20reshaping%20beauty%20standards%20and%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20can%20be%20a%20challenge%20for%20doctors%2C%20who%20have%20to%20confront%20patients%20about%20what%20is%20surgically%20achievable%20or%20physiologically%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20survey%20published%20last%20year%20by%20Beth%20Israel%20Deaconess%20Medical%20Center%20found%20that%20those%20who%20had%20experience%20using%20AI%20enhancers%20on%20photos%20had%20%26quot%3Bsignificantly%20higher%26quot%3B%20expectations%20for%20plastic%20surgery%20outcomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221123%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rachel%20Westbay%20chatgpt%20image%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a074c6aabc4e9d88574a7d7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221173%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDr.%20Rachel%20Westbay%20has%20played%20around%20with%20ChatGPT%20to%20make%20her%20own%20image.%20The%20result%3A%20a%20hand%20with%20at%20least%20six%20fingers.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Rachel%20Westbay%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20necessarily%20a%20completely%20negative%20thing%20for%20people%20to%20explore%20the%20look%20or%20the%20goal%20they%20want%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Steven%20Williams%2C%20a%20plastic%20surgeon%20in%20the%20Bay%20Area%20and%20the%20president%20of%20the%20American%20Society%20of%20Plastic%20Surgeons%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThe%20important%20thing%20is%20recognizing%20that%20there%20are%20still%20limitations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20had%20patients%20come%20in%20with%20AI-generated%20images%20of%20breast%20augmentations%2C%20body%20contouring%2C%20and%20rhinoplasties.%20His%20overriding%20take%3A%20%26quot%3BPixels%20are%20easier%20than%20surgery.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f8b9e3f3-877c-48e3-baa3-d71c7625baa9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Bodies%20aren't%20clay'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDaina%20Jenkins%20wasn't%20new%20to%20plastic%20surgery%20when%2C%20at%2060%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20have%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-33000-cosmetic-procedures-boosted-confidence-career-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20deep-plane%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-33000-cosmetic-procedures-boosted-confidence-career-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20facelift%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20it's%20sagging%2C%20bagging%2C%20or%20dragging%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20lift%20it%2C%20suck%20it%2C%20or%20tuck%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20two%20years%20of%20research%20and%20a%20consultation%2C%20she%20settled%20on%20a%20surgeon%20for%20the%20procedure%2C%20but%20he%20didn't%20provide%20images%20of%20what%20her%20after%20could%20look%20like.%20So%20she%20turned%20to%20ChatGPT%2C%20explaining%20the%20procedures%20she%20was%20planning%20and%20asking%20the%20AI%20to%20visualize%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20%E2%80%94%20pore-less%20skin%2C%20a%20sharp%20jaw%2C%20a%20particular%20pout%20%E2%80%94%20looked%20nothing%20like%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJenkins%20asked%20her%20surgeon's%20office%20about%20the%20image%20and%20was%20relieved%20to%20hear%20that%20even%20if%20she%20liked%20it%2C%20those%20results%20weren't%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Daina%20Jenkins%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a074cc694eb4c909fb2cf1a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22330%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDaina%20Jenkins%2C%20pictured%20here%20six%20months%20after%20her%20surgery%2C%20preferred%20her%20results%20to%20the%20AI-generated%20images.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Daina%20Jenkins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20wasn't%20reality%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20that%20I%20look%20natural.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20image%20generators%20tend%20to%20spit%20out%20what%20Westbay%20calls%20the%20%26quot%3BBratz%20doll%26quot%3B%20look%3A%20plumped%20lips%2C%20big%20eyes%2C%20and%20a%20defined%20jaw.%20It%20doesn't%20account%20for%20an%20individual's%20facial%20structures%2C%20different%20ethnicities%2C%20or%20for%20balancing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20gap%20between%20expectations%20and%20reality%20is%20key%20to%20AI's%20effect%20on%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20woman%20in%20her%2070s%20brought%20an%20AI-generated%20photo%20into%20a%20consultation%2C%20Dr.%20Sachin%20Shridharani%2C%20a%20plastic%20surgeon%20in%20Manhattan%2C%20said%20it%20was%20completely%20unrealistic.%20She%20was%20looking%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bsurgical%20time%20machine%26quot%3B%20and%20to%20look%20like%20her%20granddaughter%2C%20forty%20years%20her%20junior.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20explained%20that%20we%20can't%20recreate%20what%20she%20looked%20like%20when%20she%20was%20younger%2C%20but%20she%20remained%20insistent%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20AI%20can%20visualize%20certain%20features%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20nonfacial%20ones%20%E2%80%94%20quite%20well%2C%20it%20struggles%20with%20more%20complex%20procedures%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplastic-surgeon-most-common-botched-cosmetic-procedures-overdone-filler-fixes-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enose%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20follows%20are%20long%20consultations%20in%20which%20doctors%20break%20down%20what%20is%20possible%20and%20safe.%20They%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eexplain%20that%20a%20warped%20background%20suggests%20a%20filter%20was%20probably%20applied%2C%20that%20a%20specific%20nose%20tip%20would%20make%20breathing%20impossible%2C%20or%20that%20a%20waistline%20so%20narrow%20would%20mean%20there%20wouldn't%20be%20room%20for%20internal%20organs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBodies%20aren't%20clay%2C%26quot%3B%20Williams%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20physiological%20and%20organ%20systems%20that%20we%20have%20to%20protect%20when%20we're%20doing%20these%20surgeries.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20reality%20that%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-image-editing-tool-adobe-killer-test-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20images%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20impossible%20to%20recreate%20on%20the%20operating%20table%2C%20many%20of%20its%20suggestions%20wouldn't%20look%20good%20in%20real%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20procedure%20I%20can%20do%20to%20enlarge%20eye%20size%2C%26quot%3B%20Westbay%20said.%20%26quot%3BEven%20if%20we%20could%20make%20it%20happen%2C%20it%20would%20have%20people%20looking%20at%20you%20like%20a%20cartoon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20bringing%20in%20inspirational%20images%20is%20nothing%20new.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYears%20ago%2C%20patients%20would%20come%20in%20with%20a%20cutout%20photo%20from%20Vogue%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Justin%20Sacks%2C%20a%20reconstructive%20plastic%20surgeon%20at%20Washington%20University%20in%20St.%20Louis'%20medical%20school%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThat%20would%20be%20like%20a%20red%20flag%2C%20if%20you%20walked%20into%20my%20office%20and%20showed%20me%20a%20picture%20of%20Gisele%20B%C3%BCndchen%20or%20Claudia%20Schiffer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20technology%20has%20shifted%2C%20so%20have%20those%20references%2C%20with%20social%20media%20bringing%20in%20an%20influx%20of%20requests%20inspired%20by%20filters%20or%20edited%20influencers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%202019%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Estudy%20by%20the%20American%20Academy%20of%20Facial%20Plastic%20and%20Reconstructive%20Surgery%20found%20that%2072%25%20of%20facial%20plastic%20surgeons%20had%20patients%20who%20underwent%20procedures%20to%20look%20better%20in%20selfies%2C%20part%20of%20a%20phenomenon%20known%20as%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsnapchat-plastic-surgery-selfies-2018-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESnapchat%20dysmorphia%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c1a1b0d8-eff3-4b81-9905-935ae440dd0f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20AI%20upside%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20patients%20using%20AI%20may%20cause%20some%20headaches%2C%20plastic%20surgeons%20and%20dermatologists%20see%20value%20in%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESacks%2C%20who%20uses%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-doctors-use-ai-chatgpt-including-to-help-avoid-burnout-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20tools%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20digital%20scribes%20during%20appointments%2C%20said%20that%20AI%20could%20also%20improve%20the%20image%20generators%20that%20doctors%20themselves%20use%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20imagines%20working%20on%20a%20reconstruction%20for%20a%20breast%20cancer%20patient%20and%20directing%20AI%20to%20create%20live%20simulations%3A%20What%20would%20this%20patient%20look%20like%20with%20400%20milliliters%20of%20a%20silicone%20implant%3F%20What%20about%20some%20soft%20tissue%20overlay%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDo%20you%20realize%20the%20conversation%20that%20you%20would%20have%20and%20the%20expectations%20that%20you%20would%20have%20after%20that%20clinic%20visit%3F%20It%20would%20be%20astounding%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20images%20produced%20by%20AI%20or%20edited%20and%20plastered%20on%20social%20media%20have%2C%20for%20better%20or%20worse%2C%20pushed%20the%20limits%20of%20what%20surgeons%20thought%20was%20possible.%20Doctors%20are%20etching%20onto%20abdominal%20walls%20to%20create%20six%20packs%20and%20breaking%20ribs%20to%20achieve%20thinner%20waistlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20dramatic%20as%20the%20results%20may%20be%2C%20Williams%20warns%20patients%20to%20think%20about%20why%20they%20want%20a%20procedure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat's%20your%20expectation%3F%26quot%3B%20Williams%20said.%20If%20it's%20a%20new%20job%2C%20relationship%2C%20or%20social%20status%2C%20that's%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacelift-red-flags-from-plastic-surgeon-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ered%20flag%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20AI%20and%20plastic%20surgery%3F%20Contact%20his%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Amberg%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Emberg%40insider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-generated-images-chatgpt-reshape-plastic-surgery-beauty-expectations-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778925181000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a074e77ecd7cc1332bb026d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-generated-images-chatgp