s%20booming%2C%20with%20the%20bulk%20of%20sales%20fulfilled%20through%20local%20stores.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20job%20of%20picking%20items%20for%20these%20orders%20falls%20to%20store%20workers%20who%20may%20pull%20hundreds%20of%20items%20per%20shift.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhen%20a%20relatively%20small%20picking%20rule%20change%20caused%20a%20big%20stir%2C%20it%20highlighted%20the%20tension%20for%20teams.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWalmart%20has%20a%20need%20for%20speed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20retail%20giant%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-amazon-racing-to-win-retail-ecommerce-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrowing%20its%20online%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20years%2C%20fueled%20in%20large%20part%20by%20its%20ability%20to%20get%20groceries%20to%20customers%20in%20nearly%20every%20part%20of%20the%20US%20within%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20doubling%20down%20on%20digital%20is%20revealing%20some%20growing%20pains%2C%20too%2C%20as%20store%20teams%20try%20to%20balance%20this%20new%20priority%20with%20the%20traditional%20demands%20of%20operating%20a%20big%20box%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20particular%2C%20three%20workers%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20online%20business%20is%20placing%20new%20pressure%20on%20workers%20who%20are%20hustling%20to%20hit%20digital%20metrics%2C%20hauling%20increasingly%20heavy%20orders%20like%20water%20and%20mulch%2C%20and%20trying%20to%20meet%20the%20daily%20needs%20of%20their%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWalmart%20declined%20to%20comment%20for%20this%20story.%20The%20company%20is%20in%20a%20quiet%20period%20ahead%20of%20next%20week's%20scheduled%20earnings%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-retail-jobs-pay-at-amazon-costco-walmart-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWalmart%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20of%20course%2C%20are%20not%20the%20first%20to%20experience%20growing%20pains%20as%20their%20company%20expands%20its%20digital%20business.%20Target%20workers%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20company's%20emphasis%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftarget-drive-up-double-tappers-causing-chaos-and-disruption-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edigital%20order%20metrics%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20a%20daily%20source%20of%20stress%20and%20disruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20quarter%2C%20Walmart's%20e-commerce%20business%20notched%2027%25%20sales%20growth%2C%20marking%20the%20eighth%20consecutive%20quarter%20with%20growth%20over%2020%25.%20The%20bulk%20of%20those%20sales%20is%20fulfilled%20by%20employees%20at%20the%20company's%204%2C600%20US%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-sams-club-offers-enhanced-express-delivery-option-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egetting%20things%20to%20people%20faster%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20former%20CEO%20Doug%20McMillon%20said%20at%20last%20year's%20annual%20shareholder%20meeting.%20%26quot%3BDays%20are%20becoming%20hours%2C%20and%20hours%20are%20becoming%20minutes.%20Convenience%20drives%20our%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220c36ea0c-8134-40d5-9646-bcc050e897dd%5C%22%3EConvenience%20comes%20at%20a%20cost%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20former%20store%20manager%20who%20left%20the%20company%20earlier%20this%20year%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Walmart's%20focus%20and%20intensity%20on%20e-commerce%20ramped%20up%20sharply%20during%20their%20final%20year%20in%20the%20job.%20Online%20sales%20accounted%20for%20about%20a%2010th%20of%20their%20store's%20overall%20revenue%2C%20but%20required%20almost%20the%20entire%20staff%20to%20assist%20with%20fulfillment%20on%20high-volume%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20manager%20and%20an%20employee%20responsible%20for%20filling%20online%20orders%20at%20another%20location%20said%20that%20colleagues%20in%20other%20departments%20and%20store%20managers%20were%20typically%20cross-trained%20in%20digital%20and%20often%20pulled%20in%20to%20help%20fulfill%20orders%2C%20a%20distinction%20that%20highlights%20the%20importance%20of%20those%20tasks.%20Digital%20team%20members%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20weren't%20called%20on%20to%20support%20other%20departments%20nearly%20so%20often%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOrder%20volumes%20can%20range%20widely%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20uncommon%20for%20a%20worker%20to%20pick%20several%20hundred%20items%20in%20a%20shift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20so%20many%20workers%20fulfilling%20digital%20orders%20also%20means%20more%20workers%20moving%20through%20the%20aisles%20while%20focused%20on%20a%20company-owned%20mobile%20phone%2C%20which%20contains%20detailed%20order%20instructions.%20Customers%20have%20noticed.%20Several%20Business%20Insider%20readers%20over%20the%20last%20few%20weeks%20have%20emailed%20about%20Walmart%20workers%20appearing%20to%20pay%20more%20attention%20to%20their%20screens%20than%20to%20customers%20in%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20balancing%20act%20Walmart%20now%20finds%20itself%20in%20is%20perhaps%20best%20illustrated%20by%20the%20big%20stir%20that%20followed%20seemingly%20small%20rule%20changes%20about%20how%20workers%20should%20handle%20online%20order%20carts.%20The%20company%20told%20workers%20late%20last%20month%20to%20pull%20their%20carts%20so%20they%20could%20see%20where%20they%20were%20going%2C%20but%20quickly%20reversed%20course%20after%20workers%20complained%20of%20straining%20their%20shoulders%20and%20running%20over%20their%20own%20heels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20Walmart%20opted%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-changes-cart-rules-workers-pick-up-orders-safety-concerns-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esafety%20over%20order%20volume%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20instructing%20order%20pickers%20to%20push%20the%20carts%20as%20they%20had%20before%2C%20and%20instead%20reduced%20the%20number%20of%20bins%20on%20their%20carts%20from%20eight%20to%20six%20so%20they%20could%20better%20see%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20downside%20of%20having%20two%20fewer%20bins%2C%20the%20digital%20employee%20said%2C%20is%20that%20it%20is%20now%20tougher%20to%20keep%20orders%20on%20time%20when%20their%20teams%20are%20shorthanded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f7f82d74-cb01-48a2-bedc-cc73f40ac00a%5C%22%3EDemand%20and%20competition%20continue%20to%20grow%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWalmart%20is%20rolling%20out%20other%20technology%20to%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20workers%20to%20fulfill%20online%20orders%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-digital-price-tag-shelf-labels-behind-the-scenes-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edigital%20shelf%20labels%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20could%20also%20allow%20online%20order%20pickers%20to%20work%20more%20efficiently%2C%20and%20the%20company%20is%20using%20AI%20to%20make%20more%20responsive%20changes%20to%20how%20work%20is%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnline%20grocery%20sales%20aren't%20going%20anywhere%20anytime%20soon.%20Data%20from%20the%20Food%20Industry%20Association%20and%20NielsenIQ%20shows%20that%20online%20channels%20accounted%20for%20nearly%2075%25%20of%20total%20grocery%20dollar%20growth%20in%202025%2C%20with%20in-store%20sales%20remaining%20mostly%20stable.%20Online%20grocery%20sales%20are%20projected%20to%20top%20%24450%20billion%20by%202028.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20competition%20continues%20to%20heat%20up.%20Amazon%20this%20week%20expanded%20its%2030-minute%20delivery%20service%20to%20more%20US%20cities%20as%20it%20looks%20to%20counter%20Walmart's%20strength%20in%20that%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEither%20way%20you%20slice%20it%2C%20Walmart's%20online%20order%20pickers%20have%20had%20a%20busy%20year%20and%20are%20set%20to%20be%20responsible%20for%20an%20increasingly%20large%20portion%20of%20the%20stuff%20US%20shoppers%20buy%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Adreuter%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Edreuter%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20text%2Fcall%2FSignal%20at%20646-768-4750.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20WiFi%20network%2C%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20here's%20our%20guide%20to%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Esharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-online-grocery-delivery-boom-is-stretching-store-workers-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778924641000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a079dd5ecd7cc1332bb05ad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-online-grocery-delivery-boom-is-stretching-store-workers-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20relatively%20small%20Walmart%20rule%20change%20caused%20a%20big%20stir%2C%20highlighting%20the%20tension%20the%20surging%20e-commerce%20business%20is%20creating%20for%20retail%20workers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22dreuter%40businessinsider.com%20(Dominick%20Reuter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A99%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Is%20%26quot%3BJihadi%20Drug%26quot%3B%20Captagon%20Seized%20By%20India%20Under%20'Operation%20Ragepill'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22In%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Shah%20said%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20remains%20committed%20to%20building%20a%20%E2%80%9CDrug-Free%20India%E2%80%9D%20and%20maintaining%20a%20zero-tolerance%20policy%20against%20narcotics%20trafficking.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778924581000%2C%22visual%22%3A%