nts%20hesitate%20to%20set%20up%20playdates%20for%20his%20daughter%2C%20Imara%2C%20due%20to%20societal%20perceptions%20of%20him%20being%20a%20single%20dad.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gen%20Z%20are%20paying%20strangers%20around%20the%20world%20to%20send%20them%20handmade%20mail%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20holds%20huge%20piles%20of%20green%20envelopes%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a05e2ffabc4e9d88574a0b4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESnail%20mail%20clubs%20that%20cost%20around%20%2410%20a%20month%20are%20giving%20subscribers%20respite%20from%20doomscrolling.%3Cp%3EHannah%20Gustafson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMore%20and%20more%20people%20are%20signing%20up%20to%20snail%20mail%20clubs%20to%20receive%20lovingly%20curated%20letters.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAs%20people%20tire%20of%20doomscrolling%2C%20they%20are%20seeking%20out%20analog%20hobbies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESubscribers%20say%20the%20clubs%20bring%20whimsy%20and%20connection%20to%20their%20lives%2C%20all%20for%20around%20%2410.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20month%2C%20Teagan%20Franz%20counts%20down%20the%20days%20until%20a%20colorful%20envelope%20arrives%20through%20her%20letterbox.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20it%20was%20red.%20Inside%20was%20a%20handwritten%20letter%2C%20a%20tarot%20card%20featuring%20the%20Greek%20goddess%20Artemis%2C%20a%20piece%20of%20card%20scented%20with%20homemade%20essential%20oils%2C%20toad%20stool%20stickers%2C%20and%20a%20DIY%20craft%20activity%20titled%20%26quot%3Bshrine%20to%20your%20inner%20child%2C%26quot%3B%20all%20beautifully%20decorated%20in%20a%20vintage%20scrapbook%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFranz%20is%20a%20subscriber%20to%20Raindrops%20on%20Roses%2C%20a%20monthly%20spiritual%20wellness-themed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-artists-snail-mail-clubs-analogue-stable-paycheck-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esnail%20mail%20club%3C%2Fa%3E%20created%20by%20Madalin%20Giorgetta%2C%20a%2037-year-old%20nutritionist%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffitness-influencer-million-followers-madalin-giorgetta-quit-nutritionist-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eformer%20fitness%20influencer%3C%2Fa%3E%20based%20in%20Melbourne.%20Each%20letter%20costs%20%2416%20AUD%20(%2411.47).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProudly%20offline%20snail%20mail%20clubs%20like%20Giorgetta's%20are%20growing%20fast.%20Subscribers%20pay%20around%20%2410%20a%20month%20to%20receive%20a%20mailer%20on%20a%20theme%20of%20the%20sender's%20choosing%2C%20from%20cooking%20to%20poetry%20to%20fantasy%20worlds.%20Typically%2C%20the%20letters%20contain%20fun%20paper%20goodies%20like%20journal%20prompts%20and%20original%20art%20prints.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20contents%20of%20a%20snail%20mail%20club.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a05dde894eb4c909fb2c79e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMadalin%20Giorgetta's%20April%20edition%20of%20Raindrops%20of%20Roses.%3Cp%3EMadalin%20Giorgetta%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2012%20months%2C%20Google%20Trends%20data%20shows%20that%20searches%20for%20%26quot%3Bsnail%20mail%20club%26quot%3B%20increased%20by%20700%25%2C%20while%20data%20shared%20by%20Pinterest%20with%20Business%20Insider%20showed%20a%20245%25%20spike%20in%20searches%20for%20%26quot%3Bsnail%20mail%20ideas%26quot%3B%20and%20125%25%20for%20%26quot%3Bletter%20ideas%26quot%3B%20during%20the%20same%20time%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFranz%2C%20who%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffitness-influencer-madalin-giorgetta-quit-nutritionist-diet-before-after-nourishing-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ediscovered%20Giorgetta%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhen%20she%20was%20an%20influencer%2C%20likes%20the%20physicality%20of%20receiving%20something%20handmade.%20She%20said%20it%20feels%20more%20meaningful%20than%20the%20digital%20self-care%20content%20that%20she%20used%20to%20read%20a%20lot%20of%2C%20which%20was%20easily%20forgotten.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20exciting%20because%20it's%20a%20surprise%20each%20month%2C%26quot%3B%20Franz%2C%20a%2028-year-old%20content%20creator%20and%20mom-of-two%20based%20in%20Western%20Australia%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20actually%20so%20much%20fun.%20I%20don't%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20mail%20that's%20fun%20mail.%20Even%20birthday%20cards%2C%20that's%20something%20that's%20dead%20now.%20Everybody%20just%20sends%20a%20text.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaddie%20puts%20so%20much%20beautiful%20effort%20into%20her%20mail%20club%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20little%20love%20letter%2C%26quot%3B%20Franz%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20true%20that%20you're%20most%20likely%20to%20first%20encounter%20the%20trend%20online.%20But%20the%20Gen%20Z%20and%20millennial%20snail%20mail%20subscribers%20and%20creators%20who%20spoke%20to%20Business%20Insider%20said%20the%20clubs%20offer%20respite%20from%20social%20media%20feeds%20filled%20with%20impersonal%2C%20unchallenging%20%26quot%3Bbrainrot.%26quot%3B%20They%20fit%20into%20a%20wider%20movement%20of%20young%20adults%20picking%20up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flove-story-gen-z-analog-90s-nostalgia-carolyn-bessette-kennedy-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Banalog%26quot%3B%20hobbies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20like%20reading%20and%20knitting%2C%20and%20using%20retro%20tech%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fappstinence-movement-tech-lovers-dumping-smartphones-age-of-dumb-phones-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflip%20phones%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%