se%20paper%20goodie%2C%20a%20journal%20prompt%2C%20a%20Spotify%20playlist%2C%20a%20sticker%2C%20and%20an%20art%20print.%3Cp%3EHannah%20Gustafson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKatie%20Shaffer%2C%20a%2039-year-old%20diagnostic%20medical%20sonographer%20based%20in%20Houston%2C%20said%20that%20since%20signing%20up%20to%20The%20Tiny%20Post%2C%20her%20screen%20time%20is%20down%2075%25.%20Instead%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-doomscrolling-tracking-film-podcasts-books-analog-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edoomscrolling%20for%20hours%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20dark%20room%2C%20she%20spends%20her%20free%20time%20doing%20offline%20activities%20like%20crocheting%20and%20painting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20an%20instant%20gratification%20from%20a%20notification.%20It's%20sitting%20down%20and%20holding%20something%20tactile%20in%20my%20hands%20that%20makes%20me%20happy%2C%20brings%20me%20whimsy.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhimsy-trend-explained-why-it-works-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIt's%20like%20magic%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Shaffer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFebruary's%20edition%20included%20a%20QR%20code%20for%20a%20Facebook%20page%20inviting%20subscribers%20to%20%26quot%3Bfind%20a%20penpal.%26quot%3B%20Now%2C%20Schaffer%20sends%20handwritten%20letters%20and%20watercolor%20paintings%20to%20eight%20penpals%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20things%20I've%20ever%20spent%20money%20on%20and%20it%20costs%20what%2C%20less%20than%20%2412.%20It's%20so%20meaningful.%20She%20gave%20me%20my%20tiny%20community%20that%20I%20needed.%20I%20knew%20something%20had%20been%20missing%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20know%20what%20it%20was%2C%26quot%3B%20Shaffer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image.%20On%20the%20left%2C%20a%20craftsy%20mailer%2C%20on%20the%20right%2C%