ned%20across%20the%20chest%20or%20back%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20phrase%20%26quot%3BFear%20of%20God%26quot%3B%20printed%20smaller%20underneath.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%2030-year-old%20lifestyle%20reporter%20with%20an%20embarrassing%20screen-time%20average%2C%20I%20like%20to%20think%20I'm%20pretty%20in%20the%20know%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhottest-handbag-chanel-maxi-flap-trader-joes-tote-fashion-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewhat's%20trending%20with%20young%20people%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20well%20aware%20that%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwell-spent-podcast-pink-palm-puff-sweatshirt-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehoodies%20have%20transcended%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0from%20comfy%20loungewear%C2%A0you'd%20wear%20at%20home%20to%20statement%20outerwear.%20Hoodies%20and%20sweatpants%20%3Cem%3Eare%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20outfit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20same%20way%20I%20try%20to%20grasp%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flearned-gen-z-slang-connect-with-teens-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGen%20Z%20slang%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20their%20affinity%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-everyone-is-obsessed-with-stanley-cups-bottles-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etrendy%20water%20bottles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20know%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMainly%2C%20why%20is%20Fear%20of%20God%20Essentials%20so%20popular%2C%20and%20how%20are%20tweens%20convincing%20their%20parents%20to%20spend%20%24175%20on%20a%20single%20hoodie%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222309%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20wears%20a%20Fear%20of%20God%20Essentials%20hoodie.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0625b0abc4e9d88574a2cb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221732%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20man%20wears%20a%20white%20Fear%20of%20God%20Essentials%20hoodie.%3Cp%3EJeremy%20Moeller%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222d1316b0-ce8a-489d-a9ea-711e48834fbb%5C%22%3EA%20luxury%20brand%20for%20the%20masses%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAmerican%20fashion%20designer%20Jerry%20Lorenzo%20launched%20his%20clothing%20brand%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffearofgod.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFear%20of%20God%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%202013.%20It%20offered%20luxury%20basics%20inspired%20by%20gaps%20in%20his%20own%20closet%20and%20was%20named%20in%20honor%20of%20his%20Christian%20faith.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFear%20of%20God%20quickly%20became%20a%20fashion%20staple%2C%20especially%20as%20musicians%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjustin-bieber-coachella-set-review-youtube-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJustin%20Bieber%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Kanye%20West%2C%20and%20Big%20Sean%20embraced%20its%20designs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20success%20led%20Lorenzo%20to%20launch%20Fear%20of%20God%20Essentials%2C%20a%20cheaper%20%E2%80%94%20but%20still%20expensive%20%E2%80%94%20sister%20brand%20that%20focused%20on%20accessible%20streetwear%20basics%2C%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222529%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Justin%20Bieber%20wears%20a%20Fear%20of%20God%20Essentials%20set%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a048eef95396a3b6e417e72%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223100%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJustin%20Bieber%20wears%20a%20Fear%20of%20God%20Essentials%20set.%3Cp%3EBG002%2FBauer-Griffin%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20looking%20for%20bold%20colors%20and%20loud%20prints%2C%20Fear%20of%20God%20Essentials%20isn't%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20label%20strictly%20offers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-manager-dresses-up-to-work-from-home-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eneutral%20pieces%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20subtle%20graphics.%20While%20hoodies%20are%20its%20best-known%20product%2C%20Essentials%20also%20sells%20T-shirts%2C%20sweatpants%2C%20jeans%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20full%20line%20ranges%20in%20price%20from%20%2450%20to%20%24375%20per%20piece%2C%20with%20hoodies%20priced%20from%20%24130%20to%20%24200.%20The%20most%20popular%20options%20cost%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffearofgod.com%2Fcollections%2Fall-essentials%2Fproducts%2Fessentials-classic-fit-fleece-hoodie-192as262052f-homestead-heather%3F_pos%3D8%26_fid%3D5f001b0b5%26_ss%3Dc%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24150%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffearofgod.com%2Fcollections%2Fall-essentials%2Fproducts%2Fessentials-90s-hoodie-192as266991f-vintage-black%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24175%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStandard%20Fear%20of%20God%20hoodies%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20cost%20between%20%24395%20and%20%241%2C170%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a71c464d-e3e2-48c4-950c-3bd0acd34e2e%5C%22%3ETeens%2C%20tweens%2C%20and%20almost%20everyone%20else%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKinna%20Thomas%2C%20a%20mother%20of%20two%2C%20said%20it%20was%202022%20when%20her%20sons%20first%20put%20Fear%20of%20God%20Essentials%20items%20on%20their%20Christmas%20lists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20felt%20a%20little%20bit%20expensive%20for%2C%20at%20the%20time%2C%2011-%20and%2012-year-olds%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20just%20like%2C%20'Wow%2C%20what%20are%20we%20doing%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20they%20each%20unwrapped%20a%20hoodie%20on%20Christmas%20Day.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20brand%20has%20become%20a%20staple%20in%20the%20wardrobes%20of%2015-year-old%20Timmy%20and%2016-year-old%20Julian%2C%20who%20wear%20the%20sweatshirts%20at%20least%20once%20or%20twice%20a%20week%20with%20shorts%20or%20sweatpants%20and%20sneakers.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20people%20like%20it%20because%20it%20looks%20clean%20without%20doing%20too%20much%2C%26quot%3B%20Julian%20said%20of%20Essentials%20hoodies%2C%20adding%20that%20they're%20%26quot%3Breally%20popular%26quot%3B%20at%20his%20school.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20also%20like%20that%20Essentials%20doesn't%20try%20too%20hard%2C%26quot%3B%20Timmy%20added.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20simple%2C%20comfortable%2C%20and%20still%20looks%20good%2C%20which%20is%20probably%20why%20so%20many%20teenagers%20wear%20it%20all%20the%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Julian%20Thomas%20and%20Timmy%20Thomas%20wear%20Essentials%20hoodies%20before%20a%20basketball%20tournament.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a07144494eb4c909fb2ccf1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJulian%20Thomas%20and%20Timmy%20Thomas%20wear%20Essentials%20hoodies%20before%20a%20basketball%20tournament.%3Cp%3EKinna%20Thomas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Thomas%20brothers%2C%20both%20athletes%2C%20discovered%20the%20brand%20through%20their%20local%20Minneapolis%20basketball%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOri%20Nachon%2C%20a%2012-year-old%20from%20New%20York%20City%2C%20had%20a%20similar%20experience%20about%20a%20year%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20saw%20his%20basketball%20coach%20wearing%20the%20brand%20and%20told%20his%20mom%2C%20Amy%20Nachon%2C%20that%20he%20wanted%20his%20own%20Essentials%20hoodie.%20So%20she%20bought%20him%20an%20Essentials%20set%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkids-dont-need-new-things-to-go-back-to-school-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eback-to-school%20shopping%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20annoying%20how%20much%20they%20charge%20for%20them%2C%20but%20I%20guess%20I'm%20willing%20to%20pay%20it%20every%20now%20and%20then%20for%20a%20special%20item%20he%20wants%20because%20he's%20a%20good%20kid%2C%26quot%3B%20Amy%20Nachon%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ori%20Nachon%20wears%20a%20Fear%20of%20God%20Essentials%20hoodie.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a05dbfeabc4e9d88574a07d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOri%20Nachon%20wears%20a%20Fear%20of%20God%20Essentials%20hoodie.%3Cp%3EAmy%20Nachon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOri%20said%20Essentials%20is%20one%20of%20his%20%26quot%3Btop%20five%26quot%3B%20favorite%20brands%20and%20that%20it's%20extremely%20popular%20among%207th-%20and%208th-graders%20at%20his%20school.%20The%20unofficial%20tween%20uniform%20there%2C%20he%20added%2C%20includes%20Essentials%20hoodies%2C%20baggy%20sweatpants%2C%20and%20Birkenstock%20sandals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20the%20other%20%5Bhoodie%5D%20brands%20are%20too%20loud%20and%20too%20colorful.%20They%20really%20pop%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20like%20that%20Essentials%20is%20more%20chill%20and%20clean.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETake%20a%20scroll%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ftag%2Ffearofgod%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETikTok%3C%2Fa%3E%20(where%20%23fearofgod%20has%2065%2C000%20posts)%20or%20Instagram%2C%20and%20you'll%20see%20that%20this%20isn't%20a%20localized%20phenomenon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETweens%20and%20teens%20across%20the%20country%20are%20wearing%20similar%20outfits%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they're%20not%20the%20only%20demographic%20that's%20doing%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20with%20Kinna%20Thomas%2C%20I%20noticed%20that%20she%2C%20too%2C%20seemed%20fond%20of%20Fear%20of%20God.%20When%20I%20asked%20if%20she%20had%20her%20own%20Essentials%20hoodie%2C%20she%20laughed%20and%20replied%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20already%20know%20I%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20owns%20three%20Essentials%20hoodies%2C%20to%20be%20exact%2C%20and%20one%20pair%20of%20the%20brand's%20shorts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20put%20on%20this%20hoodie%2C%20and%20I%20feel%20like%20it's%20the%20coziest%20moment%20I%20have%20ever%20experienced%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fb861a33-1fc7-49a6-876b-ffa22f08e90f%5C%22%3EEssentials%20becomes%20omnipresent%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hoodie%20market%20is%20saturated.%20Brands%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpink-palm-puff-hoodie-youtube-tiktok-founder-lily-balaisis-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPink%20Palm%20Puff%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20White%20Fox%2C%20and%20Aelfric%20Eden%20are%20among%20the%20it-girls%20of%20loungewear%2C%20and%20there%20are%20countless%20others%20out%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20how%20has%20a%20brand%20known%20for%20its%20understated%20designs%20kept%20the%20attention%20of%20a%20generation%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmartphones-gen-z-creativity-attention-jonathan-haidt-anxious-generation-careers-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eshrinking%20attention%20span%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20one%20thing%2C%20Essentials%20has%20a%20slightly%20bigger%20reach%20than%20other%20brands.%20Boys%20%3Cem%3Eand%20%3C%2Fem%3Egirls%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eof%20all%20ages%20enjoy%20its%20hoodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOri%2C%20for%20example%2C%20recently%20passed%20down%20an%20Essentials%20crewneck%20that%20no%20longer%20fits%20him%20to%20his%209-year-old%20sister%20Romy%2C%20who%20is%20starting%20to%20see%20the%20brand%20become%20trendy%20within%20her%20grade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20really%20like%20knowing%20that%20%5Bthese%20hoodies%5D%20can%20be%20interchanged%20between%20boys%20and%20girls%2C%20because%20then%20we%20get%20another%20wear%20out%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Ori's%20mom%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20moms%20and%20their%20children%20also%20noted%20multiple%20times%20how%20comfortable%20Essentials%20hoodies%20are.%20They're%20oversize%20and%20made%20of%2080%25%20cotton%20and%2020%25%20polyester%20fleece.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20softness%20and%20quality%20keep%20them%20and%20other%20shoppers%20coming%20back%20year%20after%20year%20for%20new%20ones.%20Google%20Trends%20sho