%3E%3Cli%3EJulian%20Richardson%20worked%20as%20a%20flight%20attendant%20for%20Spirit%20Airlines%20for%20about%20eight%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20was%20shocked%20to%20hear%20about%20Spirit's%20shutdown%2C%20despite%20hearing%20rumors%20of%20it%20for%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20is%20relying%20on%20his%20side%20hustle%20for%20income%20while%20he%20applies%20for%20more%20flight%20attendant%20jobs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Julian%20Richardson%2C%20a%2042-year-old%20flight%20attendant%20based%20in%20Fort%20Lauderdale%2C%20Florida.%20It's%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsee-list-routes-airport-abandoned-after-spirit-shut-down-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESpirit%20flight%20attendant%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20nearly%20eight%20years.%20It%20was%20my%20first%20and%20only%20job%20as%20a%20flight%20attendant%2C%20and%20I%20definitely%20would've%20stayed%20much%20longer%20if%20I%20had%20the%20chance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20someone%20would%20get%20off%20my%20flight%20and%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20best%20flight%20I've%20ever%20had%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20made%20showing%20up%20to%20work%20every%20day%20so%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20heard%20rumors%20for%20years%20that%20Spirit%20might%20shut%20down%2C%20so%20I%20always%20knew%20it%20was%20a%20possibility.%20Still%2C%20when%20I%20woke%20up%20to%20an%20early-morning%20email%20on%20my%20phone%20from%20Spirit%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspirit-airlines-collapses-shuts-down-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eannouncing%20its%20closure%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20was%20shocked.%20I%20guess%20I%20didn't%20think%20it%20would%20actually%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20question%20mark%20in%20my%20mind%20when%20I%20think%20about%20job%20security%20as%20a%20flight%20attendant%2C%20but%20I'm%20not%20ready%20to%20give%20it%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223878f25b-afa8-4251-9f90-12ca25646351%5C%22%3EEverything%20seemed%20business-as-usual%20the%20day%20before%20Spirit%20shut%20down%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Spirit%20shut%20down%2C%20it%20seemed%20like%20everything%20just%20ceased%20to%20exist.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFortunately%2C%20I%20wasn't%20on%20a%20trip%20at%20the%20time%2C%20but%20the%20email%20said%20that%20all%20flights%20were%20canceled%2C%20and%20operations%20were%20winding%20down.%20Now%20my%20insurance%20has%20been%20halted%2C%20there%20is%20no%20severance%20pay%2C%20and%20it's%20up%20in%20the%20air%20when%20I'll%20receive%20my%20final%20paycheck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20tough%20situation%2C%20but%20I've%20managed%20my%20emotions%20by%20remembering%20that%20everything%20happens%20for%20a%20reason.%20I'm%20not%20super%20worried%20about%20losing%20my%20income%20because%20I'm%20confident%20the%20skills%20I've%20developed%20will%20help%20me%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-hired-job-search-white-collar-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efind%20another%20job%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20know%20what%20my%20next%20role%20will%20be%2C%20but%20I've%20already%20applied%20to%20airlines%20that%20have%20flight%20attendant%20openings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bfc4cfa5-f068-4b08-83af-e2891e92014b%5C%22%3EI'm%20working%20on%20my%20side-hustle%2C%20but%20I'm%20not%20ready%20to%20give%20up%20the%20benefits%20of%20being%20a%20flight%20attendant%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20making%20comedic%20skits%20on%20social%20media%20for%20a%20while%2C%20and%20it's%20definitely%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstay-at-home-mom-paying-six-figure-debt-side-hustles-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eside%20hustle%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20me.%20It's%20important%20to%20keep%20a%20side%20hustle%20for%20situations%20like%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20social%20media%20income%20can%20be%20very%20up%20and%20down%2C%20but%20right%20now%20I'm%20working%20on%20getting%20more%20brand%20deals.%20Still%2C%20I%20enjoyed%20my%20time%20at%20Spirit%2C%20and%20I%20learned%20a%20lot.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fim-flight-attendant-its-my-dream-job-but-its-lonely-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAs%20a%20flight%20attendant%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20was%20pretty%20much%20responsible%20for%20myself.%20It%20was%20up%20to%20me%20to%20wake%20up%2C%20make%20it%20to%20the%20airport%20on%20time%2C%20and%20catch%20the%20shuttle.%20It%20taught%20me%20a%20lot%20of%20independence%20and%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20I%20didn't%20experience%20any%20micromanaging%20as%20a%20flight%20attendant.%20In%20my%20experience%2C%20you%20might%20see%20your%20supervisors%20or%20managers%2C%20but%20you%20don't%20see%20them%20every%20day.%20They're%20not%20looking%20over%20your%20shoulder%20to%20see%20what%20you're%20doing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20still%20pretty%20young%2C%20and%20I%20feel%20like%20I'm%20really%20good%20at%20what%20I%20do%2C%20so%20I'd%20like%20to%20continue%20working%20as%20a%20flight%20attendant.%20Nothing%20beats%20flight%20benefits.%20I%20love%20that%20part%20of%20the%20job.%20My%20family%20and%20I%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcheap-flight-hacks-from-frequent-traveler-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etravel%20at%20a%20discounted%20rate%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20I'd%20definitely%20like%20to%20continue%20reaping%20those%20benefits.%20That%20being%20said%2C%20I'm%20open%20to%20other%20opportunities.%20I'm%20not%20naive%20enough%20to%20put%20myself%20in%20a%20box.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f053dbd8-9b8c-44e8-b807-f7beb5215b2f%5C%22%3EEventually%2C%20I%20want%20to%20own%20my%20own%20business%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnytime%20you%20work%20for%20somebody%2C%20there's%20no%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuild-skills-credentials-network-to-add-career-security-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etrue%20job%20security%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20I%20can't%20say%20I%20feel%20like%20there's%20job%20security%20as%20a%20flight%20attendant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20the%20only%20time%20you%20can%20find%20true%20job%20security%20is%20by%20working%20for%20yourself%20and%20running%20a%20business%20that%20is%20virtually%20recession-proof.%20That's%20why%20my%20long-term%20goal%20is%20to%20eventually%20own%20my%20own%20business.%20Still%2C%20I'd%20recommend%20being%20a%20flight%20attendant%20to%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20a%20flight%20attendant%20gives%20you%20a%20lot%20of%20flexibility.%20I've%20been%20able%20to%20live%20anywhere%20I%20want.%20It's%20kind%20of%20like%20a%20remote%20job%20in%20that%20way.%20I%20had%20coworkers%20who%20lived%20in%20Spain%20and%20worked%20for%2015%20days%2C%20then%20rested%20for%2015%20days.%20There%20aren't%20many%20jobs%20where%20you%20can%20do%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlight%20attendants%20also%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20interact%20with%20people%20and%20help%20them%20have%20a%20great%20experience.%20That's%20a%20part%20of%20the%20job%20I%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESpirit%20Airlines%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20this%20story.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20navigating%20job%20loss%3F%20If%20so%2C%20please%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20reporter%20at%20tmartinelli%40businessinsider.com.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-spirit-flight-attendant-shocked-at-shutdown-still-hopeful-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778923801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0724f194eb4c909fb2cd49%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-spirit-flight-attendant-shocked-at-shutdown-still-hopeful-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22