nterview-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKeep%20the%20Meter%20Running%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20several%20shows%20YouTube%20announced%20at%20its%20star-studded%20Upfronts%20presentation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYouTube%2C%20and%20its%20content%20creators%2C%20want%20their%20own%20prestige%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutube-tv-ad-budget-google-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETV%20moment%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20streaming%20service.%20You%20go%20home%2C%20you%20sit%20on%20your%20couch%2C%20you%20open%20the%20YouTube%20app%2C%20and%20you%20watch%20this%20television%20show%20the%20same%20way%20that%20you%20would%20any%20other%20television%20show%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-benefits-comedy-industry-comedians-creators-standup-diversity-finances-gatekeepers-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKareem%20Rahma%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20creator%20and%20host%20of%20%26quot%3BKeep%20the%20Meter%20Running%2C%26quot%3B%20told%20the%20packed%20theater.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECreators%2C%20like%20Rahma%20(of%20%26quot%3BSubway%20Takes%26quot%3B%20fame)%2C%20are%20ready%20to%20see%20their%20content%20taken%20as%20seriously%20as%20a%20big%20network%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20this%20is%20a%20web%20series%2C%20then%20so%20is%20every%20show%20on%20Netflix%20and%20every%20show%20on%20HBO%20Max%20because%20it's%20all%20the%20internet%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-money-explained-boy-room-adam-faze-peter-kafka-podcast-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAdam%20Faze%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20produced%20the%20show%20alongside%20Rahma.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225145%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22NEW%20YORK%2C%20NEW%20YORK%20-%20MAY%2014%3A%20Adam%20Faze%20and%20Kareem%20Rahma%20attend%20the%20%26quot%3BKeep%20The%20Meter%20Running%26quot%3B%20World%20Premiere%20at%20Metrograph%20on%20May%2014%2C%202026%20in%20New%20York%20City.%20(Photo%20by%20Daniel%20Zuchnik%2FGetty%20Images)%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a078273abc4e9d88574aa33%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223364%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAdam%20Faze%20and%20Rahma%20talked%20to%20the%20crowd%20at%20the%20%26quot%3BKeep%20the%20Meter%20Running%26quot%3B%20premiere.%3Cp%3EDaniel%20Zuchnik%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I'm%20a%20digital%20creator%2C%20then%20so%20is%20Shonda%20Rhimes%2C%26quot%3B%20Rahma%20quipped%20in%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227800e28e-0880-4dd9-8485-245d62e73924%5C%22%3EWelcome%20to%20a%20YouTube%20premiere%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELet%20me%20take%20you%20inside%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20show%2C%20in%20which%20Rahma%20tags%20along%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fcost-of-the-city%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20City%3C%2Fa%3E%20cab%20drivers%20to%20visit%20their%20favorite%20spots%2C%20premiered%20two%20episodes%20totaling%20about%2036%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20same%20show%20was%20a%20short-form%20video%20series%20on%20TikTok%20and%20Instagram.%20Now%2C%20it's%20grown%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222078%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Arriving%20at%20Keep%20the%20Meter%20Running%20premeire%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a07824494eb4c909fb2d17a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221376%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELike%20any%20premiere%2C%20there%20was%20a%20photo-op.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%2FSydney%20Bradley%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20show-branded%20merch%20and%20popcorn%2C%20as%20well%20as%20show-inspired%20cocktails%20served%20in%20classic%20New%20York%20bodega%20coffee%20cups%2C%20the%20premiere's%20reception%20brought%20together%20New%20York%20creators%2C%20media%2C%20celebrities%2C%20and%20cab%20drivers%20all%20under%20one%20roof.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20premiere%2C%20pre-paid%20yellow%20cabs%20were%20lined%20up%20outside%2C%20ready%20to%20ship%20the%20guests%20from%20the%20Metrograph%20theater%20uptown%20to%20the%20Standard%20Hotel's%20swanky%20Boom%20bar.%20Actor%20Cole%20Sprouse%20smoked%20a%20cigarette%20while%20chatting%20with%20Nico%20Heller%2C%20the%20creator%20behind%20the%20famous%20New%20York%20Nico%20Instagram%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20ushered%20into%20a%20taxi%2C%20squeezed%20between%20one%20of%20Rahma's%20cameramen%20and%20another%20journalist.%20In%20the%20front%2C%20another%20attendee%20listened%20to%20the%20driver's%20life%20story%20%E2%80%94%20emulating%20the%20show%20we%20all%20just%20watched%20on%20the%20big%20screen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222070%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Inside%20the%20taxi%20cab%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a078244abc4e9d88574aa30%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221526%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFrom%20the%20backseat%20of%20the%20cab.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%2FSydney%20Bradley%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20got%20to%20the%20after-party%20at%20Boom%2C%20we%20were%20greeted%20with%20flutes%20of%20bubbly.%20The%20venue%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20the%20Boom%20Boom%20Room%2C%20has%20hosted%20after-parties%20for%20Hollywood%20events%2C%20from%20the%20Met%20Gala%20to%20movie%20premieres.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20venue%20was%20filled%20with%20hundreds%20of%20people%2C%20including%20creator%20economy%20staples%20who%20spoke%20about%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcreators-reshaping-hollywood-youtube-netflix-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHollywood%20and%20the%20internet%3C%2Fa%3E%20blurring%20more%20than%20ever%20%E2%80%94%20some%20more%20positively%20than%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Party%20at%20Boom%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a07c17894eb4c909fb2d27e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20premiere%20after-party%20took%20place%20at%20The%20Standard%20Hotel's%20Boom%20bar.%3Cp%3EDeont%C3%A9%20Lee%2FBFA.com%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20short%20form%20vs.%20long%20form%2C%20creators%20vs.%20Hollywood%2C%20it's%20all%20one%20ecosystem%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-uta-execs-founders-schedule-talent-agency-influencers-marketing-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EZiad%20Ahmed%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20spearheads%20Gen%20Z%20marketing%20at%20talent%20agency%20UTA.%20%26quot%3BThe%20scale%20of%20the%20work%20that%20we're%20doing%20is%20much%20bigger.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20be%20relevant%20in%20culture%20today%2C%20whether%20you're%20a%20creator%20or%20a%20Hollywood%20star%2C%20%26quot%3Byou%20have%20to%20live%20on%20all%20of%20these%20screens%2C%26quot%3B%20Ahmed%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20crowd%20at%20Boom%20was%20bridging%20the%20%26quot%3Bgap%20between%20Hollywood%20and%20the%20creator%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20Jon%20Henson%2C%20who%20works%20at%20Rahma's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudio71-founders-launch-underscore-talent-management-firm-details-2021-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etalent%20management%20firm%20Underscore%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221906%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22taxi%20cab%20ice%20luge%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a078244abc4e9d88574aa31%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221490%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20after-party%20at%20Boom%20included%20a%20lit-up%20ice%20luge%20of%20a%20taxi%20cab.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%2FSydney%20Bradley%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b2037025-8f96-4082-91a5-56bc44252f0d%5C%22%3EThe%20party%20recap%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20quick%20run-down%20of%20what%20I%20saw%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20menu%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20premiere%20itself%20had%20popcorn%20and%20movie%20snacks%2C%20and%2C%20at%20the%20cocktail%20party%20reception%2C%20there%20were%20tiny%20chocolate%20chip%20cookies%20and%20hors%20d'oeuvres.%20At%20the%20after-party%2C%20slices%20of%20pizza%20were%20carried%20around%20on%20white%20paper%20plates.%20There%20were%20drinks%20upon%20arrival%2C%20a%20taxi-cab%20ice%20luge%2C%20and%20an%20open%20bar%20for%20part%20of%20the%20night.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20crowd%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAfter%20the%20two%20episodes%20aired%2C%20Rahma%20and%20Faze%20were%20interviewed%20by%20actor%20Ramy%20Youssef.%20In%20the%20crowd%20were%20Sprouse%2C%20comedian%20Eric%20Andre%2C%20rapper%20G-Eazy%2C%20UTA%20cofounder%20Jeremy%20Zimmer%2C%20and%20media%20figures%20like%20Feed%20Me's%20Emily%20Sundberg%20and%20Byline's%20Gutes%20Guterman.%20The%20various%20teams%20behind%20the%20show%20were%20also%20scattered%20throughout%2C%20including%20Another%20Normal%20Day%20(AND%20Media)%2C%20the%20studio%20that%20bankrolled%20Rahma's%20show.%20At%20the%20after-party%2C%20the%20crowd%20danced%20to%20a%20loud%20DJ%20set%2C%20but%20mostly%20mingled.%20Some%20filmed%20social%20media%20content.%20Creators%20like%20Delaney%20Rowe%20and%20Tinx%20arrived%20after%20attending%20other%20commitments%20that%20night%20(a%20Coach%20event%20and%20a%20Guggenheim%20function%2C%20respectively%2C%20per%20their%20Instagram%20stories).%20The%20party%20had%20stamina%2C%20too.%20By%20the%20time%20I%20called%20it%20quits%20a%20little%20past%201%20a.m.%2C%20it%20was%20still%20bumping.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Adam%20Faze%2C%20Kareem%20Rahma%2C%20John%20McDonagh%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a07c17894eb4c909fb2d27d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFaze%2C%20Rahma%2C%20and%20NYC%20taxi%20cab%20driver%20John%20McDonagh%20at%20Boom.%3Cp%3EDeont%C3%A9%20Lee%2FBFA.com%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20takeaway%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECreators%20want%20to%20be%20taken%20seriously.%20Grant%20Weintrob%2C%20who's%20behind%20the%20account%20Life%20on%20Film%20(with%20millions%20of%20followers)%2C%20told%20me%20creators%20like%20Rahma%20are%20setting%20the%20bar.%20They%20want%20bigger%2C%20they%20want%20better.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutube-premiere-kareem-rahma-adam-faze-keep-the-meter-running-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778922661000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a07c27f94eb4c909fb2d282%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutube-premiere-kareem-rahma-adam-faze-keep-the-meter-running-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20a%20premiere%20for%20a%20new%20YouTube-exclusive%20show%2C%20celebrities%2C%20creators%2C%20and%20taxi%20cab%20drivers%20partied%20under%20one%20roof.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sbradley%40insider.com%20(Sydney%20Bradley)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%223%20reasons%20why%20bond%20yields%20could%20keep%20surging%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22nyse%20activity%20screens%204-29%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f2b269402f8423cd99c42e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Nagle%2FBloomberg%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBond%20yields%20surged%20on%20Friday%2C%20with%20the%2010-year%20bond%20approaching%204.6%25.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20spike%20sent%20stocks%20tumbling%20on%20Friday%2C%20with%20the%20Dow%20falling%20more%20than%20500%20points.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIncoming%20Fed%20Chair%20Kevin%20Warsh's%20stance%20on%20QE%20could%20add%20to%20rising%20rate%20pressures%2C%20Morningstar%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbond-yields-treasury-bonds-stock-market-today-oil-prices-inflation-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERising%20bond%20yields%3C%2Fa%3E%20sparked%20a%20panic%20among%20investors%20on%20Friday%2C%20and%20there's%20little%20standing%20in%20the%20way%20of%20a%20deeper%20bond-market%20rout%2C%20according%20Dominic%20Pappalardo%2C%20the%20chief%20multi-asset%20strategist%20at%20Morningstar%20Wealth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYields%20on%2030-year%20Treasurys%20have%20surged%20above%205%25%20in%20recent%20weeks%2C%20while%20rates%20on%20the%2010-year%20have%20risen%20more%20than%2020%20basis%20points%20since%20the%20start%20of%20May%20to%204.59%25.%20The%20spike%20sent%20stocks%20tumbling%20from%20records%20notched%20earlier%20in%20the%20week%2C%20with%20the%20Dow%20dropping%20more%20than%20500%20point%20and%20the%20Nasdaq%20and%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20losing%20more%20than%201%25.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FRsELH%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22396%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Pappalardo%2C%20three%20factors%20are%20driving%20the%20move%2C%20which%20he%20believes%20will%20remain%20in%20place%20to%20push%20yields%20even%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20first%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20the%20most%20obvious%3A%20investors%20are%20worried%20that%20surging%20oil%20prices%20driven%20by%20the%20US-Iran%20war%20will%20trigger%20another%20bout%20of%20inflation.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finflation-april-cpi-stock-market-reaction-fed-rate-hikes-economy-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EApril's%20CPI%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20showed%20a%203.8%25%20jump%20in%20consumer%20prices%20year-over-year%2C%20the%20most%20since%202023%2C%20thanks%20in%20large%20part%20to%20rising%20energy%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20longer%20the%20war%20goes%20on%20and%20oil%20prices%20stay%20elevated%2C%20the%20more%20investors%20grow%20concerned%20that%20inflation%20will%20become%20entrenched.%20This%20causes%20bond%20investors%20to%20demand%20more%20compensation%20through%20higher%20yields.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20were%20fully%20reopened%20today%2C%20Pappalardo%20said%20it%20would%20take%20at%20least%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20to%20rebuild%20production%20infrastructure%20and%20have%20oil%20flows%20back%20to%20full%20capacity%2C%20meaning%20oil%20prices%20are%20set%20to%20stay%20elevated%20for%20the%20foreseeable%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecond%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20higher%20rates%20from%20elevated%20oil%20prices%20create%20a%20knock-on%20effect%20in%20the%20Treasury%20market%20that%20can%20stimulate%20rates%20to%20rise%20further%2C%20Pappalardo%20said.%20Rising%20interest%20rates%20due%20to%20inflation%20fears%20US%20borrowing%20costs%20rise%2C%20which%20will%20spur%20the%20even%20more%20bond%20issuance%20to%20cover%20the%20government's%20debt%20service.%20Increased%20bond%20supply%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20can%20translate%20into%20higher%20yields%2C%20creating%20a%20negative%20feedback%20loop%20of%20more%20borrowing%20and%20higher%20costs.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThird%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20adding%20fuel%20to%20the%20fire%20is%20incoming%20Federal%20Reserve%20Chair%20Kevin%20Warsh's%20prior%20statements%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkevin-warsh-fed-chair-nomination-reactions-economists-business-leaders-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eopposing%20the%20expansion%20of%20the%20Fed's%20balance%20sheet%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20its%20buying%20of%20assets.%20If%20the%20Fed%20stops%20buying%20Treasurys%2C%20it%20could%20send%20yields%20higher%20by%20removing%20a%20source%20of%20demand%20from%20the%20market.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20definitely%20think%20yields%20could%20go%20higher%2C%20particularly%20on%20the%20long%20end%2C%26quot%3B%20Pappalardo%20told%20Business%20Insider%20on%20Friday.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20hard%20really%20to%20identify%20the%20catalyst%20that%20would%20cause%20yields%20to%20come%20down.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3B5%25%20would%20not%20be%20shocking%20to%20me%20on%20the%2010-year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPappalardo%20said%20that%20rising%20long-term%20yields%20would%20generally%20be%20bad%20for%20stocks%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20growth%20stocks%20%E2%80%94%20as%20they%20weigh%20on%20the%20value%20of%20companies'%20future%20earnings%20as%20investors%20compare%20them%20against%20a%20risk-free%20rate.%20Higher%20rates%20also%20mean%20companies%20need%20to%20issue%20debt%20at%20higher%20rates%2C%20increasing%20their%20borrowing%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20hurts%20corporate%20fundamentals%2C%20it%20makes%2C%20future%20investment%20less%20likely%2C%20so%20it%2C%20it%20really%20just%20stifles%20growth%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20ways%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20at%20an%20index%20level%2C%20Pappalardo%20said%20it's%20difficult%20to%20know%20how%20higher%20rates%20will%20impact%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%2C%20as%20the%20strength%20of%20the%20AI%20trade%20continues%20to%20fuel%20gains.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-are-bond-yields-rising-interest-rates-treasury-bonds-inflation-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778922601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a077b14abc4e9d88574a9d8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-are-bond-yields-rising-interest-rates-trea