20same%20package%20repeatedly.%20Bill%20Atienza%2C%2029%2C%20helped%20older%20Americans%2C%20including%20his%20parents%2C%20improve%20their%20technology%20skills%20through%20vibe-coded%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsecretly-working-remote-jobs-overeremployed-tech-layoffs-millennial-overemployment-income-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etech%20support%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20one%20woman%20created%20an%20app%20with%20his%20help%20that%20allows%20her%20to%20speak%20with%20her%20late%20husband%20after%20uploading%20his%20voice%20into%20Perplexity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%229302%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pratik%20Desai%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0783d994eb4c909fb2d190%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%226201%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDesai%20built%20a%20no-code%20workflow%20for%20his%20mother%20but%20is%20developing%20a%20more%20advanced%20version.%3Cp%3ECorrie%20Aune%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDesai's%20no-code%20solution%20couldn't%20keep%20up%20with%20his%20mother's%201%2C600%20pages%20of%20notes%2C%20and%20he%20used%20his%20existing%20tech%20savvy%20to%20build%20a%20more%20complex%20system.%20He%20believes%20his%20workflow%20saved%20her%20life%20three%20times.%20She%20lived%20for%2076%20days%20after%20her%20diagnosis%20before%20dying%20at%2067.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20biggest%20concern%20was%20how%20do%20I%20get%20her%20as%20much%20time%20as%20possible%20with%20as%20much%20quality%20as%20possible%3F%26quot%3B%20Desai%20said%2C%20standing%20next%20to%20his%20father%2C%20Subhash%2C%20in%20the%20family's%20living%20room.%20%26quot%3BNot%20only%20did%20we%20not%20have%20the%20time%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20emotional%20side%2C%20it%20felt%20immediately%20like%20I%20had%20to%20vibe%20code%20something%20and%20manifest%20it%20into%20existence%20that%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228e4d74d5-f8df-4267-903d-c13b68eb1ed8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaking%20life%20more%20accessible%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Lazar%2C%20director%20of%20The%20Health%2C%20Aging%2C%20and%20Technology%20Lab%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Maryland%2C%20said%20that%20vibe%20coding%20offers%20families%20a%20way%20to%20access%20customized%20tools%20that%20help%20ease%20a%20complex%20and%20varied%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20always%20issues%20with%20these%20kinds%20of%20systems%2C%20and%20there%20is%20never%20a%20single%20solution%2C%20but%20it%20shows%20a%20real%20need%20and%20the%20level%20of%20customization%20and%20personalization%20that%20people%20need%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224570%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Matt%20Sanner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a07827f94eb4c909fb2d180%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223656%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMatt%20Sanner%20vibe%20coded%20an%20app%20to%20help%20his%20parents%20identify%20scams.%3Cp%3EZack%20Wittman%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDanesh%20Davar%2C%2036%2C%20watched%20as%20his%20mother%20suffered%20several%20hemorrhages%20in%202019%2C%20losing%20some%20motor%20function%2C%20including%20her%20ability%20to%20type.%20Davar%20couldn't%20find%20dictation%20tools%20that%20fit%20her%20needs%20for%20under%20%24500%20a%20year.%20After%20taking%20a%202.5-hour%20vibe%20coding%20tutorial%2C%20he%20left%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanagers-are-in-charge-of-making-you-use-ai-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIT%20management%3C%2Fa%3E%20job%20and%20built%20an%20app%20he%20later%20called%20Talkativ.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20working%20on%20smaller%20projects%20on%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faging-scam-victims-caregiving-retirement-vibe-coding-cursor-reddit-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20vibe-coding%20platform%20Cursor%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Davar%2C%20based%20in%20London%2C%20began%20integrating%20more%20advanced%20features%20into%20the%20platform%2C%20which%20he%20built%20for%20about%20%24200.%20The%20first%20two%20versions%20didn't%20work%20well%2C%20he%20said%2C%20though%20he%20got%20the%20desktop%20app%20to%20dictate%20words%20in%20all%20text%20boxes%20and%20apps%2C%20read%20in%20over%2050%20languages%2C%20and%20incorporate%20auto-punctuation%20and%20formatting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20zero%20ad%20spend%2C%20Talkativ%20reached%20200%20sign-ups%20in%20its%20first%20three%20months%20and%20processed%20over%2012%2C000%20successful%20dictations.%20Most%20importantly%2C%20his%20mom%2C%20who%20retired%20a%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20has%20used%20the%20system%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe's%20a%20rock%20star%20and%20very%20resilient%20in%20that%20if%20she%20puts%20her%20mind%20to%20something%2C%20she%20will%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Davar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVibe%20coding%20can%20%E2%80%94%20and%20often%20does%20%E2%80%94%20go%20awry.%20Without%20technical%20acumen%2C%20many%20vibe%20coders%20struggle%20to%20detect%20errors%20in%20the%20code%20or%20to%20maintain%20code%2C%20which%20often%20requires%20periodic%20updates%20as%20software%20changes%2C%20for%20example.%20Vibe%20coding%20can%20introduce%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flovable-security-access-vibe-coding-projects-risk-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esecurity%20vulnerabilities%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20personal%20information%20has%20leaked%20to%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20vibe%20coders%20told%20Business%20Insider%20they%20worried%20their%20creations%2C%20if%20expanded%20on%20a%20broader%20scale%20without%20developer%20input%2C%20could%20backfire.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3D36c16a643b6af45d02ecbd4025579566bf3e5638c8842cfaf756559394bb39a0%26postID%3D6a076d66ea9599c045f3aee7%26postSlug%3Delder-care-dementia-cancer-ai-vibe-coding-claude-lovable-cursor-2026-5%26tags%3Dservic