2image-caption%5C%22%3E%5CnSrdjan%20Stakic%20has%20grown%20his%20vibe-coded%20system%20into%20a%20startup%20called%20Alvis.%C2%A0%5Cn%3Cspan%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-source%5C%22%3E%5CnIan%20Tuttle%20for%20BI%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20first%20used%20AI%20to%20generate%20summaries%20of%20his%20and%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-seniors-to-mexico-long-term-care-costs-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emedical%20care%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20wanted%20a%20system%20that%20could%20ethically%20observe%20them%20if%20he%20wasn't%20home%20with%20them.%20He%20turned%20to%20Gemini%20and%20ChatGPT%20to%20brainstorm%20his%20idea%20while%20consulting%20his%20parents%20about%20scenarios%20such%20as%20a%20medical%20emergency%20or%20a%20fall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20train%20the%20AI%20tool%20he%20built%20on%20Lovable%2C%20he%20uploaded%20training%20videos%20for%20nurses%20and%20healthcare%20workers.%20He%20built%20an%20AI%20equipped%20with%20cameras%20to%20detect%20falls%2C%20but%20he%20hired%20an%20IT%20company%20to%20help%20him%20connect%20multiple%20cameras.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20vibe%20coded%20the%20system%20to%20send%20notifications%20to%20loved%20ones%20or%20EMS%20workers%2C%20clipping%20footage%20from%20the%20incident%20and%20including%20their%20location%20and%20a%20summary%20of%20their%20health%20records.%20He's%20building%20the%20system%20to%20be%20more%20robust%20as%20part%20of%20his%20startup%2C%20Alvis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20amazing%20to%20see%20how%20vibe%20coding%20is%20democratizing%20access%20to%20AI%20tools%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Stakic%2C%20in%20California.%20%26quot%3BI%20still%20don't%20fully%20understand%20code%20or%20the%20extent%20of%20what%20I%20built%2C%20but%20it%20seems%20to%20be%20working.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDesai%2C%20who%20built%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-healthcare-companies-can-prepare-data-for-ai-assisted-management-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emedical%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20workflow%20for%20his%20mother's%20cancer%2C%20and%20his%20father%2C%20Subhash%2C%20stood%20in%20their%20living%20room%20glancing%20at%20a%20photo%20of%20Smruti.%20She%20was%20the%20matriarch%20of%20the%20family%20and%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bforce%20of%20presence%2C%26quot%3B%20Desai%20recalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228450%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pratik%20Desai%20and%20his%20father%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a077b1d94eb4c909fb2d123%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225633%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDesai%20and%20his%20father%20have%20adjusted%20to%20life%20after%20the%20death%20of%20Smruti.%3Cp%3ECorrie%20Aune%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20hearing%20from%20friends%20and%20colleagues%20who%20said%20his%20tool%20could%20help%20them%2C%20Desai%20is%20programming%20a%20free%20version.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20is%20still%2C%20of%20course%2C%20subject%20to%20error%20and%20can%20put%20those%20without%20existing%20tech%20skills%20down%20the%20wrong%20path%2C%20but%20even%20so%2C%20it%20opens%20the%20door%20to%20more%20options%20for%20caregivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20able%20to%20ask%20the%20right%20questions%20and%20push%20her%20doctors%20to%20do%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20Desai%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStaying%20beside%20the%20bed%20where%20Smruti%20lived%20out%20her%20final%20days%2C%20Desai%20checked%20his%20phone.%20Messages%20from%20work%20poured%20in.%20One%20was%20from%20a%20colleague%20who%20wanted%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20going%20to%20change%20people's%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20Desai%20said%20as%20his%20father%20nodded%20in%20approval.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felder-care-dementia-cancer-ai-vibe-coding-claude-lovable-