he%20bagels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20about%2022%20people%2C%20and%20everyone%20takes%20the%20orders%2C%20makes%20the%20bagels%2C%20and%20does%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20always%20have%20to%20recreate%20the%20wheel%20to%20stay%20competitive.%20Social%20media%20is%20where%20you%20need%20to%20be.%20I'm%20not%20naive%20to%20it%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20a%20stronger%20part%20of%20my%20experiences.%20So%2C%20I'm%20learning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20I've%20had%20great%20employees%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0i.e.%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-brands-are-working-with-college-students-as-nano-influencers-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecollege%20students%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0who%20love%20social%20media%20themselves%2C%20so%20they're%20happy%20to%20take%20it%20on.%20It'd%20be%20good%20for%20a%20few%20months%2C%20but%20then%20the%20rest%20of%20their%20lives%20come%20into%20place%2C%20and%20it%20wasn't%20a%20full-time%20job.%20It%20would%20slowly%20die.%20We'd%20get%20along%20fine%2C%20but%20then%20I'd%20throw%20another%20person%20on%2C%20and%20the%20same%20thing%20would%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222e793b00-d011-479b-b761-cd255c707766%5C%22%3EWhy%20I%20used%20AI%20for%20our%20shop's%20social%20media%20posts%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20pointed%20to%20a%20company%20that%20helps%20small%20businesses%20with%20AI.%20It%20helps%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ai-is-changing-job-applications-and-hiring-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehuman%20resources%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20have%20a%20paid%20accountant%20and%20bookkeeper.%20They%20can%20give%20me%20their%20analysis%2C%20but%20why%20not%20have%20a%20third%20opinion%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20program%20does%20many%20different%20aspects%20of%20business%2C%20and%20one%20is%20social%20media.%20It%20was%20nice.%20There's%20a%20calendar%20where%20you%20can%20build%20a%20whole%20month%20of%20posts%20to%20release%20on%20Instagram.%20We're%20a%20college%20town%2C%20so%20graduation%20is%20coming%20up.%20I'd%20ask%3A%20What's%20a%20neat%20spin%20on%20a%20post%20about%20graduation%20to%20encourage%20someone%20to%20come%20in%3F%20The%20program%20comes%20up%20with%20an%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20allows%20us%20to%20import%20our%20photos%20that%20we've%20taken%2C%20and%20it%20uses%20those%2C%20but%20it%20can%20tweak%20them.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPart%20of%20the%20picture%20was%20real.%20I%20looked%20at%20it%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNot%20too%20bad.%26quot%3B%20Some%20of%20the%20AI%20bagels%20they%20had%20in%20the%20background%20didn't%20look%20like%20ours%2C%20and%20I%20would%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BCan%20you%20make%20that%20smaller%20and%20thinner%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20didn't%20take%20long%20for%20our%20audience%20to%20realize%20what%20we%20were%20posting%20wasn't%20100%25%20Myer's.%20I%20appreciate%20their%20passion%20for%20us%20not%20doing%20this%20the%20way%20they'd%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22One%20of%20Myer's%20Bagels%20social%20media%20posts%20that%20was%20edited%20with%20AI%20is%20pictured.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a074ab2ecd7cc1332bb0231%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAI%20turned%20an%20online%20review%20for%20Myer's%20Bagels%20into%20a%20handwritten%20note.%3Cp%3EMyer's%20Bagels%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20had%20a%20picture%20of%20our%20retail%20bags%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efor%20the%20grocery%20store.%20Those%20were%20actually%20our%20photos%20of%20the%20bags.%20The%20AI%20went%20into%20our%20Google%2C%20Yelp%2C%20or%20old%20Instagram%20comments%20and%20pulled%20out%20a%20review%20from%20Sam.%20It%20put%20our%20bags%20in%20front%20of%20a%20wood%20fire%20that%20wasn't%20our%20fire%2C%20and%20took%20that%20quote%20and%20made%20a%20fake%20handwritten%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWas%20it%20untruthful%3F%20Yes.%20Was%20it%20our%20fire%2C%20image%2C%20and%20background%3F%20No.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-ads-2011-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFor%20McDonald's%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20anyone%20else%20who's%20advertising%20food%2C%20it's%20in%20a%20studio.%20But%20Sam%20is%20a%20real%20person.%20Sam%20made%20that%20quote%2C%20and%20those%20were%20our%20bags.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20a%20picture%20that%20we'd%20used%20before%20of%20our%20baker%20rolling%20out%20the%20dough.%20AI%20took%20that%20photo%2C%20superimposed%20it%20on%20a%20nice%20wooden%20cutting%20board%2C%20and%20then%20put%20a%20fire%20in%20the%20background%20and%20a%20kettle%20to%20boil%20bagels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20not%20how%20we're%20laid%20out%2C%20and%20our%20customers%20know%20that.%20But%20it%20was%20our%20real%20bagels%2C%20real%20hands%2C%20real%20dough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20AI-edited%20photo%20posted%20to%20social%20media%20from%20Myer's%20Bagels%20is%20pictured.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a074ae8ecd7cc1332bb0235%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAI%20generated%20a%20new%20layout%20of%20the%20Myer's%20Bagels%20retail%20store%2C%20something%20customers%20noticed.%3Cp%3EMyer's%20Bagels%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20those%20two%20photos%2C%20I%20bet%20there%20were%2025-30%20comments%20for%20each%20one%2C%20plus%20people%20replying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20some%20very%20passionate%2C%20adamant%20people%20who%20went%20to%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fgoogle-reviews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20reviews%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20left%20us%20one%20star%2C%20claiming%20nothing%20about%20the%20food%2C%20just%20about%20this%20situation.%20No%20one%20called%20us%20directly%3B%20it%20was%20more%20of%20a%20response%20through%20social%20media.%20The%20pen%20is%20mightier%20than%20the%20sword.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20a%20few%20people%20who%20went%20in%20to%20defend%20us%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BLook%2C%20they're%20a%20small%20business.%20They%20just%20wanted%20to%20be%20more%20creative.%26quot%3B%20I%20appreciate%20those%20comments%2C%20but%20certainly%20the%20negative%20responses%20were%20much%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20were%20very%20civil%2C%20others%20I%20would%20classify%20as%20not%20very%20civil.%20I%20don't%20judge%20on%20that%20part.%20The%20medium%20allows%20it%2C%20and%20for%20us%20to%20be%20on%20it%2C%20you%20have%20to%20be%20ready%20to%20respond%20or%20fall%20victim%20to%20whatever%20you%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c82e2c8e-b496-45a4-a63e-fc9c9685c419%5C%22%3EI%20apologized%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0but%20I'm%20not%20anti-AI%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20got%20quite%20a%20bit%20of%20feedback%20on%20a%20few%20posts.%20I%20went%20in%2C%20pulled%20them%2C%20and%20apologized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wasn't%20married%20to%20the%20idea.%20It%20was%20a%20test%2C%20or%20the%20first%20foot%20forward.%20So%2C%20I%20was%20willing%20to%20erase%20them%20and%20say%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20do%20better.%20We've%20heard.%26quot%3B%20It's%20just%20like%2C%20if%20people%20don't%20like%20a%20bagel%20flavor%20and%20it%20doesn't%20sell%2C%20we%20will%20make%20a%20new%20bagel%20flavor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDX4eUuIlMD7%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDX4eUuIlMD7%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2F