%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A96%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Foperation-epic-fury-to-resume-donald-trump-weighs-fresh-iran-strikes-after-china-visit-report%2Farticleshow%2F131131463.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Foperation-epic-fury-to-resume-donald-trump-weighs-fresh-iran-strikes-after-china-visit-report%2Famp_articleshow%2F131131463.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Foperation-epic-fury-to-resume-donald-trump-weighs-fresh-iran-strikes-after-china-visit-report%2Famp_articleshow%2F131131463.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22My%20dad%20died%20of%20cancer%20at%2058.%20My%20family%20used%20some%20of%20his%20insurance%20money%20to%20go%20on%20a%20cruise%2C%20and%20it%20helped%20us%20grieve%20and%20connect.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22737%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20pictured%20at%20a%20port%20with%20her%20mom%20and%20sister.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a03466858810e27922acb56%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22553%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20said%20traveling%20with%20her%20family%20after%20her%20dad%20passed%20away%20helped%20them%20grieve.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Shea%20Karssing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAfter%20my%20dad%20died%2C%20my%20mom%20used%20part%20of%20his%20life%20insurance%20payout%20to%20take%20a%20family%20trip.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20mom%2C%20sister%2C%20and%20I%20took%20a%207-day%20cruise%20that%20visited%20several%20Mediterranean%20cities.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20wasn't%20our%20typical%20vacation%2C%20but%20it%20helped%20my%20family%20reconnect%20without%20the%20stress%20of%20planning.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdad-died-before-retirement-changed-how-i-live-risk-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edad%20died%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20prostate%20cancer.%20He%20was%2056%2C%20and%20I%20was%2025%20at%20the%20time.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ELosing%20him%20made%20my%20family%20realize%20how%20short%20our%20time%20on%20this%20earth%20%E2%80%94%20and%20our%20time%20together%20%E2%80%94%20really%20is.%20With%20part%20of%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Flife-insurance%2Fbest-life-insurance-companies%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elife%20insurance%20%3C%2Fa%3Epayout%2C%20my%20mom%20decided%20to%20take%20my%20sister%20and%20me%20on%20a%20vacation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20us%20had%20ever%20considered%20a%20cruise.%20The%20idea%20always%20seemed%20tacky%20and%20commercial%20to%20us.%20But%20cruising%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-skeptical-loved-first-cruise-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eaffordable%20way%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20us%20to%20travel%20internationally%20%E2%80%94%20and%2C%20as%20we%20learned%2C%20a%20more%20peaceful%20way%20for%20us%20to%20grieve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221493729f-3ac1-49a9-b0b6-81ca2f190a13%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20were%20never%20%26quot%3Bcruise%20people%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20family%20had%20never%20been%20on%20a%20cruise%20together.%20If%20I'm%20being%20honest%2C%20it%20wasn't%20really%20our%20type%20of%20thing.%20We%20were%20more%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bstay%20in%20the%20self-catering%20chalet%20and%20drive%20yourselves%20on%20safari%26quot%3B%20kind%20of%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-things-to-do-in-south-africa-2015-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20South%20Africa%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20my%20dad%20worked%20for%20a%20government%20organization%20that%20maintained%20wildlife%20conservation%20areas.%20We%20could%20stay%20in%20these%20areas%20for%20free%2C%20so%20almost%20all%20of%20our%20family%20vacation%20time%20consisted%20of%20self-catered%20stays%20in%20basic%20accommodation%20in%20some%20of%20the%20wildest%20and%20most%20beautiful%20places%20in%20the%20country.%20It%20was%20a%20privilege%20that%20I%20can%20only%20fully%20appreciate%20now%20as%20an%20adult.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20my%20dad%20passed%20away%2C%20my%20mom%20decided%20to%20use%20some%20of%20the%20money%20from%20his%20life%20insurance%20policy%20for%20us%20girls%20to%20celebrate%20his%20life.%20We%20knew%20we%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20different%20and%20memorable%20%E2%80%94%20the%20kind%20of%20vacation%20we'd%20never%20been%20able%20to%20take%20as%20a%20family%20of%20four.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20a%20cruise%20was%20the%20furthest%20thing%20from%20our%20minds.%20We%20pictured%20them%20as%20crowded%20and%20commercial%20%E2%80%94%20the%20exact%20opposite%20of%20how%20we'd%20always%20traveled.%20But%20the%20price%20was%20right%2C%20and%20not%20wanting%20to%20invest%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftake-trips-on-late-father-birthday-grief-travel-helps-us-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eplanning%20something%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20we%20were%20grieving%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20go%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20poses%20with%20her%20mom%20and%20sister.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0347347c7e83f26041ac2c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22670%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20said%20being%20on%20a%20cruise%20allowed%20her%20family%20to%20focus%20on%20their%20connection%20instead%20of%20where%20they%20were%20going%20or%20what%20they%20were%20going%20to%20eat%20next.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Shea%20Karssing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ed5c93bc-7f13-4dce-bddd-760f1d3222b1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20the%20easiest%20kind%20of%20travel%20we'd%20ever%20done%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20we%20went%20on%20our%20voyage.%20The%20three%20of%20us%20visited%20six%20Mediterranean%20cities%20over%20seven%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20accommodation%2C%20meals%2C%20and%20transport%20between%20countries%20bundled%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcheap-caribbean-cruise-costa-pacifica-review-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eone%20upfront%20cost%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20was%20significantly%20cheaper%20than%20any%20land-based%20trip%20we%20could%20have%20planned.%20And%20the%20real%20value%20wasn't%20financial%3B%20it%20was%20practical%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20traveling%2C%20but%20it's%20certainly%20not%20stress-free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20this%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%2C%20we%20need%20to%20get%20on%20this%20bus.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWait%2C%20who's%20got%20the%20passports%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETensions%20only%20escalate%20when%20family%20is%20involved%2C%20especially%20when%20everyone%20is%20carrying%20their%20grief%20with%20them%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229543d93c-b867-4c5a-9b68-85ae91e18242%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20cruise%20lightened%20the%20mental%20load%20of%20a%20difficult%20trip%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWithout%20the%20daily%20decision-making%20drama%20of%20where%20to%20eat%2C%20where%20to%20go%2C%20and%20how%20to%20get%20there%2C%20we%20spent%20more%20time%20actually%20enjoying%20one%20another's%20company%2C%20which%20is%20what%20Dad%20would%20have%20wanted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20all%20navigating%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fliving-with-family-as-adult-not-going-backward-helped-grief-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eour%20own%20versions%20of%20grief%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%20my%20dad%20died%2C%20we%20could%20just%20be%20together%20without%20needing%20to%20manage%20anything%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20those%20people%20we%20used%20to%20roll%20our%20eyes%20at%2C%20we%20attended%20all%20the%20evening%20shows%2C%20joined%20the%20morning%20aerobics%20on%20the%20deck%2C%20spent%20hours%20people-watching%2C%20and%20got%20my%20mom%20hooked%20on%20strawberry%20daiquiris%20(the%20virgin%20ones%2C%20because%20they%20were%20cheaper).%20Looking%20back%2C%20I%20think%20those%20moments%20mattered%20more%20than%20any%20destination%20we%20visited%20during%20the%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20poses%20with%20her%20mom%20and%20sister%20while%20enjoying%20daiquiris%20on%20a%20Mediterranean%20cruise.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0346ec95396a3b6e4176dc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22827%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhile%20the%20family%20has%20not%20been%20on%20another%20cruise%2C%20they%20have%20taken%20to%20enjoying%20virgin%20strawberry%20daiquiris%20on%20recent%20trips%20together.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Shea%20Karssing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2200688fbe-2683-4b8a-92a2-9dc961ff3146%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20didn't%20become%20%26quot%3Bcruise%20people%26quot%3B%20after%20that%2C%20but%20we%20understood%20the%20appeal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20my%20dad's%20death%2C%20my%20mom%20fought%20to%20keep%20the%20free%20accommodation%20at%20the%20conservation%20areas.%20My%20sister%20now%20lives%20in%20Dubai%2C%20and%20whenever%20she%20comes%20home%2C%20we%20go%20back%20to%20those%20same%20self-catering%2C%20DIY%20stays%20that%20hold%20so%20many%20memories%20of%20Dad.%20This%20time%2C%20with%20homemade%20strawberry%20daiquiris%20in%20hand.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWho%20would%20have%20thought%20that%20a%20cruise%20could%20give%20us%20the%20space%20to%20appreciate%20those%20old%20family%20trips%20in%20a%20completely%20new%20way%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsi