ent%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFeature%20image%20courtesy%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shutterstock.com%2Fimage-photo%2Ftagetes-erecta-aztec-marigold-mexican-big-2403544919%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%20afternoons%2C%20when%20the%20monsoon%20loosens%20its%20grip%20and%20the%20air%20smells%20faintly%20of%20drying%20earth%2C%20gardens%20across%20India%20quietly%20prepare%20for%20a%20burst%20of%20colour.%20If%20you%20grew%20up%20in%20an%20Indian%20home%2C%20you%20might%20remember%20this%20season%20not%20by%20calendars%20but%20by%20your%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%20hands%2C%20busy%20pushing%20tiny%20marigold%20saplings%20into%20the%20soil.%20By%20winter%2C%20her%20garden%20would%20be%20crowned%20with%20golden-orange%20blooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20families%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F442021%2Flearn-marigold-farming-steps-from-expert-arup-kumar-ghosh-simple-process-farming-business-flower%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emarigolds%20%3C%2Fa%3Eare%20more%20than%20flowers%20%E2%80%94%20they%20are%20memories%20woven%20into%20rituals%2C%20markers%20of%20festivals%2C%20and%20a%20constant%20presence%20in%20Indian%20households.%20October%20was%20always%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20month%20of%20marigolds%E2%80%9D%2C%20when%20every%20backyard%2C%20balcony%20pot%2C%20or%20courtyard%20seemed%20to%20await%20its%20share%20of%20yellow%20and%20saffron.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A493791%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Ftbi-showcase%2F%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%