ew%20farming%20industry%20but%20also%20exemplify%20the%20potential%20for%20agri-business%20entrepreneurship%20to%20drive%20economic%20growth%20in%20rural%20communities.%20I%20am%20glad%20that%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20wet%20produce%20anymore%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20photos%3A%20Brijith%20Krishnan%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcashew.icar.gov.in%2Faicrpc%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2FStatus-of-Cashew-Research-.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Status%20of%20Cashew%20Research%20and%20Development%20in%20India%3A%20A%20State%20Perspective%20%3C%2Fa%3Epublished%20by%20Dr%20M%20Gangadhara%20Nayak%2C%20Director%2C%20ICAR-Directorate%20of%20Cashew%20Research%2C%20Karnataka%20in%20November%202018.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757147400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-1-1725551491.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D496857%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kerala-based%20farmer%20Brijith%20Krishnan%20started%20Eatery%20Malbarikas%20which%20makes%20dishes%20using%20sprouted%20cashew%20nuts.%20Interestingly%2C%20he%20enhanced%20the%20germination%20potential%20of%20cashews%20and%20helps%20fellow%20cashew%20farmers%20as%20well.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F496857%2Fkerala-farmer-wet-cashews-value-added-products%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Rs%205000%20Budget%20Guide%20to%20Exploring%20Karnala%E2%80%99s%20Forests%2C%20Fort%20%26amp%3B%20Birdlife%2C%20Just%20an%20Hour%20From%20Mumbai%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVisual