ations%20will%20go%20towards%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1)%20airlifting%20the%20boats%20to%20the%20sites%20of%20rescue%20operations%20and%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2)%20procuring%20relief%20material%20so%20that%20families%20can%20be%20helped%20once%20they%20are%20shifted%20to%20the%20relief%20centres.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donatekart.com%2FDisaster-Relief%2FThe-Better-India%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Clabel%3EDONATE%20NOW%20%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20943px)%20100vw%2C%20943px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FScreenshot-2025-09-05-173515-1757073937.png%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22943%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20relief%20requirements%20by%20the%20people%20who%20are%20being%20sheltered%20at%20camps%20after%20being%20rescued%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FScreenshot-2025-09-05-173515-1757073937.png%20943w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FScreenshot-2025-09-05-173515-1757073937-300x219.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FScreenshot-2025-09-05-173515-1757073937-500x365.png%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FScreenshot-2025-09-05-173515-1757073937-768x560.png%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FScreenshot-2025-09-05-173515-1757073937-150x109.png%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496953%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22688%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20relief%20requirements%20of%20the%20people%20who%20are%20being%20sheltered%20at%20camps%20after%20being%20rescued%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%