0kitchen%20gets%20messy%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20more%20likely%20to%20eat%20the%20food%20they%20helped%20make.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPlanting%20seeds%20for%20the%20future%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChildhood%20is%20fleeting%2C%20but%20its%20foundations%20last%20a%20lifetime.%20By%20the%20age%20of%20five%2C%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20brain%20is%20already%2090%25%20developed.%20The%20foods%20parents%20offer%20in%20these%20early%20years%20%E2%80%94%20say%20millet%20%3Cem%3Edosas%20%3C%2Fem%3Einstead%20of%20instant%20noodles%2C%20microgreen%20salads%20instead%20of%20fries%20%E2%80%94%20quietly%20shape%20not%20just%20health%2C%20but%20focus%2C%20mood%2C%20and%20resilience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2FAjay-growing-microgreens-in-racks-and-food-grade-trays-under-in-a-controlled-environment-1669988504.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Microgreens%20in%20food%20grade%20trays%20are%20grown%20in%20controlled%20environment.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2FAjay-growing-microgreens-in-racks-and-food-grade-trays-under-in-a-controlled-environment-1669988504.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2FAjay-growing-microgreens-in-racks-and-food-grade-trays-under-in-a-controlled-environment-1669988504-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2FAjay-growing-microgreens-in-racks-and-food-grade-trays-under-in-a-controlled-environment-1669988504-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2FAjay-growing-microgreens-in-racks-and-food-grade-trays-under-in-a-controlled-environment-1669988504-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterind